<h1>Update User Information</h1>

<p>System administrators can update user information in the radiology information system.</p>
<p>Enter the user name and click the "<span class="code">GO</span>" button. System administrators will be able to manage user's account. </p>

<p>You can change any of the following fields:</p>

<ul>
	<li>User Name</li>
	<li>Password</li>
	<li>User Class(type in one of a,d,p,r)*</li>
</ul>

<p>* <span class="code">a, d, p, and r stand for Administrator, Doctor, Radiologist and Patient, respectively</span>.</br>

<p>Click the "<span class="code">OK</span>" button to save the changes. Click the "cancel" button to cancel the registration.</p>

